{"tid":1458201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲打識得計粒鋼珠要幾大","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:31:06.000Z","uid":188544,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"af0dac502c3eba790abc565ab7d37ad4abddc6d7","tid":1458201,"uid":188544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:17:05.000Z","msg":"先可以做到一個人眼鞏膜破裂、晶體受損<br />\n上頜骨、鼻骨有骨折?<br />\n<br />\n根據中央電視台所講, 琴晚有人畀降珠整傷隻眼, 首先用一粒鐵珠可以做成上頷骨，鼻骨骨折，粒珠要幾大先到做到咁嘅傷害，另外射珠嗰個人又要有幾大力先至做到咁嘅傷害？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQ8R0U3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQ8R0U3.png&h=846ecaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返直播短片, 揸住吖叉嘅人大概嘅位置係68米<br />\n<br />\n 小弟才疏學淺, 只係知要好大力同埋粒珠要有咁上下大細先可以做成咁嘅傷害。<br />\n他實在計唔到 粒珠要幾重幾大<br />\n但知道高手在民間, 煩請各位巴絲打幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n做完之後文宣就可以做長輩圖話返畀其他人知cctv講大話"},{"pid":"c20a8a291ae6f2ea2e3a918433d31f460a4dbcc9","tid":1458201,"uid":259530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be777c6f819e8cb8f9da15fea00165dac0b68e09","tid":1458201,"uid":265786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"推 不過央視講既野咁荒謬 真係智障先會信"},{"pid":"94a4544b018cfc651ac5a4295b2dc270838fdb48","tid":1458201,"uid":188544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be777c6f819e8cb8f9da15fea00165dac0b68e09","tid":1458201,"uid":265786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"推 不過央視講既野咁荒謬 真係智障先會信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVbsAbu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVbsAbu.jpg&h=18f2f305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最慘係對家紋身已經開始做緊嘢<br />\n我哋的一班和理非(我認我係和理非)仲喺度大聲唱今天我"},{"pid":"56b8c620c3764ff8bb06c6d7596831a188b12a92","tid":1458201,"uid":134226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"